{"result":{"contents":["\u0060\u0060\u0060csharp\nstring[] File.ReadAllLines(string path) (\u002B 1 overload)\n\u0060\u0060\u0060","Opens a text file, reads all lines of the file, and then closes the file\\.","Returns:\n\n  A string array containing all lines of the file\\.\n\n","Exceptions:\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060csharp\n  ArgumentException\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060csharp\n  ArgumentNullException\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060csharp\n  PathTooLongException\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060csharp\n  DirectoryNotFoundException\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060csharp\n  IOException\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060csharp\n  UnauthorizedAccessException\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060csharp\n  FileNotFoundException\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060csharp\n  NotSupportedException\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060csharp\n  System.Security.SecurityException\n\u0060\u0060\u0060"]},"id":442,"type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
